サンペドロとパロスバーデスの丘に日が沈む。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="San Pedro" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The sun sets over the San Pedro and Palos Verdes hills. サンペドロの夕日 サンペドロとパロスバーデスの丘に日が沈む。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2407_DSC_0191.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2407_DSC_0191.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Depot</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240714/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Depot" /><published>2024-07-14T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2024-07-14T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/depot</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240714/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The Depot in old town Torrance. A century ago it was the city train depot; it was remade into a restaurant. But the train track is still in occasional use.
 </p>
  
  <p class="jp">
<!--<span class="title_jp">デポ</span>-->
トーランスの旧市街にある「ザ・デポ」。100年前は市の列車発着場だったが、レストランに改装された。しかし、線路は今でも時々使われている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Architecture" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The Depot in old town Torrance. A century ago it was the city train depot; it was remade into a restaurant. But the train track is still in occasional use. トーランスの旧市街にある「ザ・デポ」。100年前は市の列車発着場だったが、レストランに改装された。しかし、線路は今でも時々使われている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2407_DSC_0139_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2407_DSC_0139_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Blanketed by Fog</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240712/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Blanketed by Fog" /><published>2024-07-12T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2024-07-12T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/blanket</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240712/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
It really is a blanket of fog out there. Rare to be in a position to see where the fog stops.
 </p>
  
  <p class="jp">
