</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Clouds" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[At Del Cerro Park on the cliffs of the Palos Verdes Peninsula, looking down at the clouds completely covering the ocean. In the distance is Catalina Island. 雲の上 パロスバーデス半島の断崖にあるデルセロ公園で、海をすっぽりと覆う雲を見下ろしながら。遠くにカタリナ島。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2407_DSC_0105_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2407_DSC_0105_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Cloudy Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240709/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cloudy Beach" /><published>2024-07-09T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2024-07-09T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/riviera</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240709/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
